# Figma Design File Structure

## 1. Frame Setup
- Dimensions: 1440px × 5000px (scrollable)
- Grid: 12-column (1170px content width)
- Margins: 24px sides
- Padding: 48px between sections

## 2. Color Styles
- Primary: #0B5ED7
- Secondary: #212529
- Accent: #DC3545
- Background: #F8F9FA
- Text: #212529 (dark), #6C757D (muted)
- White: #FFFFFF
- Success: #28A745

## 3. Text Styles
- H1: Inter Bold 48px
- H2: Inter Bold 36px
- H3: Inter Bold 24px
- Body: Inter Regular 16px
- Small: Inter Regular 14px
- Button: Inter Medium 14px (all caps)

## 4. Components Created

### A. Navigation Bar
- Logo: CameraVN with camera icon
- Main menu items with dropdown arrows
- Search bar with icon
- Cart icon with badge
- User profile icon
- Mobile hamburger menu variant

### B. Hero Section
- Background: Unsplash camera image with overlay
- Headline: "Chụp lại khoảnh khắc"
- Subhead: "với công nghệ hàng đầu"
- CTA Buttons: 
  - Primary: "Mua ngay" 
  - Secondary: "Dịch vụ"

### C. Category Cards (6)
- Icons: Camera, CameraFill, CameraVideo, Disc, Lightning, Tools
- Category names
- Hover effect: scale(1.05) + shadow

### D. Product Cards (6)
- Product image placeholder
- Name and rating (4.8 ★)
- Price with discount strikethrough
- "Thêm vào giỏ" button
- Sale badge (-15%)
- Hover: lift + shadow

### E. Promotional Banner
- Dark background with gradient
- Headline: "Khuyến mãi đặc biệt tháng 3"
- Countdown timer (days, hours, minutes, seconds)
- CTA Button: "Mua ngay"

### F. Testimonial Cards (3)
- Avatar initials (NT, TH, PL)
- 5-star rating
- Testimonial text
- Customer name + title

### G. Newsletter Section
- Blue background
- Headline: "Đăng ký nhận thông tin"
- Email input field
- Subscribe button

### H. Footer
- 4-column layout
- About section
- Quick links
- Customer service
- Contact info
- Copyright notice

## 5. Interactive Elements

### A. Shopping Cart Modal
- Product rows with:
  - Thumbnail
  - Name
  - Price
  - Quantity controls
- Subtotal calculation
- Checkout button

### B. Login/Register Modals
- Form fields:
  - Email
  - Password
  - Remember me checkbox
- Toggle link between forms
- Social login options

## 6. Responsive Breakpoints

### A. Tablet (768px)
- 2-column product grid
- Stacked footer
- Simplified navigation

### B. Mobile (375px)
- 1-column layout
- Hamburger menu
- Larger tap targets
- Adjusted typography

## 7. Export Assets
- Product card component
- Color palette
- Typography scale
- Icon set (Bootstrap Icons)

## 8. Prototype Flows
1. Homepage → Product → Add to Cart
2. Navigation → Category → Filtering
3. Cart → Checkout process
4. User login/registration

## Implementation Notes:
1. Used Unsplash images for product placeholders
2. Created consistent spacing system (8px baseline)
3. Designed all interactive states (hover, active, disabled)
4. Included error states for forms
5. Added loading skeletons for async content